However, the paper also discusses the regularity and interestingness of functions computed by deep networks, which suggests a connection to sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper introduces new techniques and bounds, which could be relevant to the sub-category cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
